{"tid":45375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最貴冤獄？男子探監變坐監 關32小時賠465萬","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T03:56:38.000Z","uid":10874,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4959bbaa5ce352e4023c64bef1eeacf027aa6f17","tid":45375,"uid":10874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"美國芝加哥一名男子去監獄探監，被錯誤鎖在一個囚室內32小時，最後獲獄方賠償約465萬港元，平均1小時獲賠14萬5千港元，創下當地最短時間冤獄的最高賠償紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n這名「探監變坐監」的男子名叫法拉（Farad Polk），他因為兒子犯毒被判坐監，早前到獄中探望兒子，但法拉在到獄室時，不知為何竟迷路，錯誤地去到一間空置的囚室，並被反鎖在裡面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U63A41h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU63A41h.jpg&h=7ea74cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法拉在囚室裡曾喊救命，但無任何人發現，他在斷水斷糧的情況下，被困囚室32小時，最後他撬開天花灑水系統，觸動消防系統，驚動消防員到場，獄方這時才派員到囚室營救他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/102946_8df460e38332285d95fde85d3fde7c15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F102946_8df460e38332285d95fde85d3fde7c15.jpg&h=805edd78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法拉其後控告監獄，並獲賠償60萬美元(約465萬港元)和解，據美國傳媒報導，這賠償金額，創下當地最短時間冤獄的最高賠償紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9/1652926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9%2F1652926&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=e92224d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9/1652926</a>"},{"pid":"9278d790c720b07b918a947f847912e8b3bb6357","tid":45375,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"睇黎發達唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b83b8b45e61e2e359afe71bbe94a9a81dccd069","tid":45375,"uid":445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎發達唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq