066","tid":45375,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"所以點解讀programming成日都提住你end-users are stupid<br />\n寫lab report要由walk the reader through<br />\n千其唔好有任何assumption<br />\n因為呢個世界總有班懵撚用你想像唔到嘅方法嚟搞劈屎出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過亦都多得呢班on9美帝嘅說明書係公認數一數二地好 寫得好撚詳細甚至圖文並茂"},{"pid":"70abf818d3cab70d8adabe398cf28da76d80d5cc","tid":45375,"uid":20373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國芝加哥一名男子去監獄探監，被錯誤鎖在一個囚室內32小時，最後獲獄方賠償約465萬港元，平均1小時獲賠14萬5千港元，創下當地最短時間冤獄的最高賠償紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n這名「探監變坐監」的男子名叫<span style=\"color: red;\">法拉</span>（Farad Polk），他因為兒子犯毒被判坐監，早前到獄中探望兒子，但法拉在到獄室時，不知為何竟迷路，錯誤地去到一間空置的囚室，並被反鎖在裡面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U63A41h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU63A41h.jpg&h=7ea74cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法拉在囚室裡曾喊救命，但無任何人發現，他在斷水斷糧的情況下，被困囚室32小時，最後他撬開天花灑水系統，觸動消防系統，驚動消防員到場，獄方這時才派員到囚室營救他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/102946_8df460e38332285d95fde85d3fde7c15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F102946_8df460e38332285d95fde85d3fde7c15.jpg&h=805edd78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法拉其後控告監獄，並獲賠償60萬美元(約465萬港元)和解，據美國傳媒報導，這賠償金額，創下當地最短時間冤獄的最高賠償紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9/1652926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9%2F1652926&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=e92224d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9/1652926</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}